model":"","maxCrew":4,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::d51ce65a-b3ed-11ed-b35b-325096b39f47","name":"Bonifacio","coordinates":{"latitude":41.38905215189958,"longitude":9.15999176158211},"country":"France"},"cruisingCapacity":10,"staticCapacity":0,"builtYear":2008,"architect":"","interiorDesigner":"Sunreef Yachts","refitYear":2023,"topSpeed":10,"cruiseSpeed":8,"fuelCapacity":60,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Double Cabins","value":"3"},{"label":"Twin Cabin","value":"1"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":0,"length":21.4,"beam":10.9,"draft":1.9,"hullType":"Catamaran","hullConstruction":"GRP","tonnage":87,"superStructure":["Flybridge"],"engines":"2x 240Hp Diesel Yanmar,","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"}],"toys":[{"label":"Seabob","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Wakeboard","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Water Ski","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Sublue","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Paddleboards","quantity":"2"},{"label":"Banana Boat","quantity":"1"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"},{"label":" Snorkeling Gear"},{"label":" Swim Platform"}],"entertainment":["WiFi connection"]},"crew":[{"name":"Vladimir Orel","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cccc07-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::bf539600-3420-11f1-ad37-eb68f0c1d2d1/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Ukrainian\nLanguages: Italian, English, Russian, Ukrainian\n\nCaptain Vladimir  is an experienced charter captain with over 7 years of expertise operating sailing catamarans up to 80ft across the Mediterranean and Seychelles. Known for his strong leadership and calm, professional approach, he ensures safe navigation while delivering a high standard of service on board. \n\nHaving worked extensively with renowned brands such as Sunreef, Lagoon, Fountaine Pajot, and Bali, Volodymyr combines solid technical knowledge with a keen focus on guest satisfaction and smooth crew coordination. \n\nMultilingual and highly adaptable, he speaks English, Italian, Ukrainian, and Russian, making communication seamless with international guests. His attention to detail, positive attitude, and dedication to excellence ensure every charter is both safe and memorable."},{"name":"Bahatim Yilmaz","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::9938368400::vessel::d5cccc07-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f3f23290-3420-11f1-ad37-eb68f0c1d2d1/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Turkish\nLanguages: Turkish, English\n\nBahattin is a dedicated and hardworking deckhand with over 4 years of experience on both private and charter yachts up to 40m. He has developed strong practical skills in deck operations, including anchoring, mooring, tender driving, teak maintenance, and polishing, ensuring the vessel is always maintained to a high standard.\n\nKnown for his positive attitude and strong work ethic, Bahattin thrives in fast-paced environments and is highly reliable when it comes to supporting both crew and guests. His attention to detail, team spirit, and proactive approach make him a valuable asset on board. \n\nHe is also experienced in watersports activities such as jet skiing, parasailing, and supporting guests during water-based operations, contributing to a fun and safe onboard experience.\n\nHe holds several yachting certifications, including IYT Master of Yachts 200T (Power) and RIB Master, and is committed to continuously developing his skills within the industry."},{"name":"TBC ","role":"Captain"},{"name":"TBC","role":"Captain"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":2800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":2800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":3800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Summer 2026: Low Season","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2026-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-06-13T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2027-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2027-06-13T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2028-01-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2028-06-13T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-09-16T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-12-31T23:5